column5: Anyone on this site know of an outfitter out of Int Falls that will fly a small group to a private camp? The camp is located in the Woodland Caribou Pro Park. Thank you
Here are two you can try: http://rustymyers.com/ http://northernwilderness.net/lakes

You could also check out:Kenora Air Service - KenoraSlate Falls Airways - Sioux LookoutHidden Bay - Sioux LookoutNorthwest Flying - Nestor FallsNestor Falls Airways - Nestor FallsPipestone Air - EmoRoss Air - Emo
